    proofTheoreticHypersequentGraftCompositionStep_preserves_derivable
      (hn.proof_theoretic_graft_composition_mono_base
        hbase hstep)
      (derivableHypersequent_mono hbase hG)

/--
Main-result form of the sequent-shadow accounting theorem.  The theorem is
only a shadow statement: it records the consumed inserted proof component, but
the derivation-level graft is still supplied by the proof-tree labels and
